<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Self-assessment requested</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#fafafa;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#3f3f46;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background:#fafafa;padding:32px 0;">
<tr><td align="center">
<table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e4e4e7;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;">
<tr><td style="padding:24px 32px;background:#ffffff;">
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td style="vertical-align:middle;padding-right:12px;">
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
<tr><td width="40" height="40" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#1c1917" style="background:#1c1917;background-image:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c1917,#292524);border-radius:12px;">
<img src="cid:{{logoCid}}" width="28" height="28" alt="Intra" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;">
</td></tr>
</table>
</td>
<td style="vertical-align:middle;">
<div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#0a0a0a;line-height:1;">Intra</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:4px;">360° Feedback Service</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="height:3px;background:#db2777;background-image:linear-gradient(90deg,#db2777,#f59e0b,#d97706);font-size:0;line-height:0;">&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:32px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3f46;">
<h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#0a0a0a;">Hi {{rateeFirstName}},</h1>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px;">A new 360° feedback review has been created for you{{#if cycleTitle}} as part of the <strong style="color:#0a0a0a;">{{cycleTitle}}</strong> cycle{{/if}}.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px;">Please complete your self-assessment. It is the first step before respondents are invited to share their feedback.</p>
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="margin:24px 0;">
<tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#1c1917" style="background:#1c1917;background-image:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c1917,#292524);border-radius:9999px;">
<a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 28px;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Start self-assessment</a>
</td></tr>
</table>
<p style="margin:0;color:#71717a;font-size:13px;">If the button doesn't work, copy this link into your browser:<br><a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="color:#0a0a0a;word-break:break-all;text-decoration:underline;">{{actionUrl}}</a></p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background:#fafafa;border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7;padding:20px 32px;font-size:12px;color:#71717a;line-height:1.5;">
You received this email because you participate in a 360° feedback review at Intra. If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color:#0a0a0a;text-decoration:underline;">{{supportEmail}}</a>.
</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
